# Deliberate cost-vs-security tradeoffs for a solo-developer, free-tier-first
# project (see CLAUDE.md's Cost Management Philosophy) - not oversights.

# S3 buckets use SSE-S3 (AES256, free) instead of SSE-KMS with a customer-
# managed key (~$1/month/key + per-request charges). AES256 already encrypts
# data at rest; a CMK only adds key-rotation/audit control this project has
# no requirement for.
AVD-AWS-0132

# CloudFront has no AWS WAF in front of it (~$5-6/month base + per-rule +
# per-request charges) - not justified for a low-traffic personal finance
# app's static frontend distribution.
AVD-AWS-0011
